  - Ah, young traveler. I have been waiting for you. Will you stay a while and listen?
  - Thanks! I knew you'd help
  - 'Oh. Okay. '
  - There is a red packet that must reach the king. It is of great importance.
  - Take this and deliver it safely. You will be rewarded.
